highlights.text: “לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 78 spots at #119.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “ראיתי עולם” is the highest at #8.
“דאמ” by Jasmin Moallem is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #142.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 336 weeks straight.
